# image-to-text
convert image to text by baidu API.  Includes mobile phone number and email address currently.

Email addresses supported are as follows:
- 126.com
- qq.com
- 163.com
- gmail.com
- sina.com
- hotmail.com
- outlook.com


# Usage(support for windows only)
